\end_inset

, they claimed 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta\Delta\mu\sim-2E_{reorg}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset

 Therefore, it will be also interesting to clarify the influence of electronic
 relaxation of the solute, before applying QM-RISM hybrid method energetically
